@page "/about-us"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>About Us</PageTitle>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px auto; max-width: 800px; background-color: #f3f2f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #4b0082; margin-bottom: 20px;">About Us</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">
        At <strong>PawfectMatch</strong>, we are dedicated to connecting loving families with rescue dogs in need of forever homes.
        Our mission is to give every dog a second chance at happiness by providing compassionate care, thorough adoption processes,
        and ongoing support to ensure successful matches between pets and their new families.
    </p>
</div>

<div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 30px; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 400px;">
        <img src="Images/dog1.jpg" alt="Riley, a happy adopted dog" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);">
        <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 1rem; color: #FFFFFF;">Riley, an older dog who found a new home through PawfectMatch.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 400px;">
        <img src="Images/dog2.jpg" alt="A happy adopted dog" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);">
        <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 1rem; color: #FFFFFF;">A senior dog enjoying life with a new family thanks to PawfectMatch.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px auto; max-width: 800px; background-color: #f3f2f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">
        Founded in 2015, <strong>PawfectMatch</strong> began with a simple mission: to connect loving families with rescue dogs in need of a forever home.
        With a deep passion for animal welfare, we work tirelessly to ensure each adoption is a perfect match, creating bonds that last a lifetime.
    </p>
</div>
